data.title: Devilman: Devilman (TV Anime Version)
data.meta_description:
Devilman from the classic 1972-73 TV anime of the same name is now a resin figure kit from Hasegawa! He's been sculpted in a standing pose with his devil wings extended, and decals are included for his eyes. Order this iconic character for your own collection today!

Description

This is a fixed-pose, resin-cast kit of a science-fiction/anime item.

Devilman from the classic 1972-73 TV anime of the same name is now a resin figure kit from Hasegawa! He's been sculpted in a standing pose with his devil wings extended, and decals are included for his eyes. Order this iconic character for your own collection today!

[Size]: Approximately 14cm tall (not including wings) when completed

[Materials]: Resin

[Includes]: Decals
